{
 "name": "RPlog_Dibar_Tyler_over_Etti_IV",
 "title": "Running the Blockade Over Etti IV",
 "summary": "Trapped on Etti IV as the Corporate Sector Authority's picket fleet closes a blockade around the planet, veteran Corellian ace Tyler 'Fossil' Damion and his astromech Nate lead the slower Lambda shuttle of mercenary Dibar 'Adder' and his droid Leet on a desperate run for the single gap in the cordon, guarded by a Golan battle station. Tyler threads the gap using proton torpedoes to mask their passage in proton gas while the pirate corvette Night Scourge, commanded by Paladin, charges in with B-wings, bombers, and a gunship to draw fire and batter the station's shields. Dibar's shuttle takes heavy damage, losing a dorsal fin and suffering an onboard fire he must fight by hand while Leet flies the ship, but Tyler doubles back to share shields and clear the pursuing fighters. With Paladin's group covering the retreat, both fugitives and the entire pirate force break free and jump to the Smuggler's Run trade route. The escape succeeds, leaving the CSA blockade outwitted and Paladin's Loose Cannons taunting them over the comm.",
